export default function diff(t,e){let p=[];for(const f in t)if(f in e)if(t[f]&&"object"==typeof t[f]){const n=diff(t[f],e[f]);p.push(...n.map(t=>(t.path.unshift(f),t)))}else t[f]!==e[f]&&p.push({path:[f],type:"CHANGE",value:e[f]});else p.push({type:"REMOVE",path:[f]});for(const i in e)i in t||p.push({type:"CREATE",path:[i],value:e[i]});return p}